text:
Are mera bhai hentai ğŸ™ƒ..
Pretty sure maine tereko hentai bulana nhi shuru kiya tha do not blame me, although mai tereko bhot easily blame kar sakta hu for pari wala photo viral karna wing me aur behen wala harkat shuru karne ke liye. bhot kuch hai likhne ke liye yaar tere liye to starting from 1st year summers jab we actually came to know each other well uske phle to it was mostly formal talk types... tmhari baat karni ki speed aur style me training lena padta hai logo ko to understand what u are trying to say but iss chiz me mastery hai mereko hehe... first year summer project was one of the highlights wo roz roz ke nightouts and then tmhari first and the only gpl jisme ro diye the tm (sorry uske liye ğŸ˜›ğŸ˜› ). Then u started watching animes  isme bhi mera influence tha iska credit le sakte hai hm ğŸ˜¬ğŸ˜¬ğŸ˜.. U are really easy to talk to the only person jiske room pe hm raat ko 3 baje bas aise hi aa jate the kuki kuch karne ko nhi hota tha and then we used to talk about so many animes till breakfast ya atleast dawn.. another highlight would be wo subah 4-5 baje ka cold weather me badminton not because hmlog jaldi uth gaye the but because hmlog uss waqt club se wapas aate the ya flying se wapas aate the... yaar ye sab khatam ho gaya still aisa lag rha ki aaj raat wapas nightout maarne jana hai...  You are probably one of the most caring persons i know and utne hi chutiye bhi ho for the very same reason... Iske alawa wo bombay and delhi wale trips has to be a major highlight in our  college lifes. Plus wo delhi wala to alag hi scene ho gaya tha but kaafi maza aaya tha udhar bhi apan teen log hi sirf gaye the (that was epic)... Teckriti ke phle one night before design change and plane wapas banane ka frustration bhi ek memory hi ban gaya hai ab to... Plus tm galaxy me bhi the saath me jisme kaam bhigadte zada the tm and then fraud marne lagte the tm aur sarthak aur anjesh .. Last ke days bhi apan bhot time saath rhe the and bhot baate kari thi tmhare saath pata hi nhi chalta tha kaise time paar ho gaya... College shuru hua tha to lagta tha kya bhai bhai bana rhe sabko but abhi ekdum brother from another mother wali feel aati hai terese.. tu jis din gaya tha wo din bhi bhot emotional day tha ğŸ¥º...  Yaar tereko pareshaan karna bhot miss karenge but chill hai apne anime talks will go on and i seriously want to meet u soon i good health till then take care aur all the best... cheers ğŸ¥‚.. miss you ğŸ–¤ğŸ–¤
